text.tspan: LEC was unable to hold onto an advantage built through T1/T2 and the first few 'S' curves (T3-T4). PIA couldn't recover from a
big moment in T1/T2. NOR out braked himself into the casio triangle (T16/17). Overall, VER's consistent lap prevailed.
